# Curated mini pci.ids for xps13-9350 (Dell XPS 13 9350, Lunar Lake-M).
# Contains only the vendor/device/subsystem entries present in this machine's sysfs.
# Extracted from the upstream pci.ids database; entries not yet upstream are hand-authored
# from lspci -nn output captured on the live machine.
